{"tid":2411780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"20萬網紅仿妝「像到根本複製貼上」　泫雅本人一看火速認證了！","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T05:54:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3d2abd0c084c115d6a7312a814544e725d3245","tid":2411780,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"南韓女星泫雅2020年因健康惡化，休息了近半年的時間，日前終於以主打歌《I'm Not Cool》回歸樂壇，不只歌曲本身受到討論，就連她在MV、打歌舞台上的服裝造型都引起風潮，大陸更有一位美妝博主拍攝了仿妝影片，相似程度讓大批網友讚嘆，就連泫雅本人都現身認證，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457198.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457198.jpg&h=37585679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457199.jpg&h=fbf256e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅日前發行《I'm Not Cool》回歸樂壇。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／hyunah_aa）<br />\n<br />\n大陸一名美妝博主「哈哈少女Chic」在Bilibili影音平台上有超過20萬名粉絲追蹤，平常常會拍一些化妝、穿搭以及Vlog影片，受到許多少女喜愛，其中最著名的便是泫雅的仿妝，幾乎每個妝容都有拍過仿妝影片，她在自我介紹中也表示自己有「通州泫雅」之稱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457194.jpg&h=60f74336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網紅「哈哈少女Chic」以仿妝泫雅出名。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／choichicc）<br />\n<br />\n近日，「哈哈少女Chic」拍攝了一段泫雅新歌《I'm Not Cool》的仿妝影片，只見她照著MV裡的造型，將髮型整理成短瀏海搭配雙辮子，戴上華麗的項鍊與黑色蕾絲水鑽手套，粉紅色的眼妝上還有亮片點綴，最後擦上桃紅色的口紅，各種細節都模仿得相當到位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457193.jpg&h=6a324a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457195.jpg&h=ac5d43a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「哈哈少女Chic」近日又仿妝了泫雅新歌《I'm Not Cool》。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／choichicc）<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，「哈哈少女Chic」也將自己仿妝後的照片貼上Instagram，高超的化妝技巧加上肢體動作，每個角度都跟泫雅十分相似，讓大批網友看了都讚嘆連連，紛紛留言「根本是複製貼上」、「可能連泫雅自己都生不出這麼像的人」、「走在南韓街頭可能會被包圍的程度，實在太像了」，就連泫雅本人看到都忍不住按讚認證，立刻掀起許多粉絲熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457197.jpg&h=ee7844d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「哈哈少女Chic」仿妝太像，連泫雅都現身認證。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／choichicc）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/5457200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2F5457200.jpg&h=a3294094&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bef5c63e3b4e10979b86987144e825ac83f11d33","tid":2411780,"uid":238828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"熄左濾鏡先講野啦"},{"pid":"e952e6a039c687cad2fe5476503895c59982ab94","tid":2411780,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈"},{"pid":"7c0ea1f2ef60cfbc8b6966a95ec97fc83ce697f3","tid":2411780,"uid":308570,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T21:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R36O5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R36O5b.png&h=d0926195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淡妝靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50758af2d3f8f3fdefbf005310aa16f520fa8530","tid":2411780,"uid":181319,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"7c0ea1f2ef60cfbc8b6966a95ec97fc83ce697f3","tid":2411780,"uid":308570,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T21:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R36O5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R36O5b.png&h=d0926195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淡妝靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:50:28.0